  35,26,Subsequently ja punished those disbelieved ako hrozny bol Moj retribution
  35,27,Ona nie realize GOD sends nadol sky zavlazit whereby my produce robit ovocie z various colors Vecer mountains have inak colors peaks je biely red some inaksie color ravens bol cierny
