  35,37,They scream therein Our Lord ona get us out z tu my zavodny righteousness robota my pouzivat robi my nie dat ona life-long chance continuous reminders those berie heed Ona nie receive warner? Therefore chut (consequences). transgressors have ziaden 1 pomoc them
